-- Seed data reference
-- The full sample dataset is generated by scripts/generate_sample_data.py and loaded
-- by scripts/setup_database.py so that the CSV and SQLite database stay consistent.
--
-- Direct SQLite CLI import into business_metrics is not recommended because the
-- table includes generated id and created_at columns. Use the Python setup
-- script so the CSV columns are mapped correctly.
--
-- Preferred command:
-- python scripts/setup_database.py
